es.ull.isaatc.simulation.core
Interface TimeDrivenActivity

All Superinterfaces:
Activity, java.lang.Comparable<SimulationObject>, Describable, Identifiable, Prioritizable, SimulationObject, VariableStore, VariableStoreSimulationObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
TimeDrivenActivity, TimeDrivenActivity
public interface TimeDrivenActivity
extends Activity

An Activity whose finalization is driven by a timestamp, i.e. the activity starts when there are enough resources and finishes after a period of time.

Author:
Iván Castilla Rodríguez
